itemDescription: Officer of the British Royal Navy (1783-1874)

wikipedia_page.main: Admiral Sir Henry Prescott  (4 May 1783 – 18 November 1874) was an officer of the British Royal Navy who served during the French Revolutionary and Napoleonic Wars, and was later the Governor of the Newfoundland Colony.
